CHECK:UNNECESSARY_PARENTHESES: Unnecessary parentheses around hotplug_slot_info->adapter_status
#156: FILE: drivers/pci/hotplug/shpchp_core.c:164:
+			&(hotplug_slot_info->adapter_status));

WARNING:SPLIT_STRING: quoted string split across lines
#159: FILE: drivers/pci/hotplug/shpchp_core.c:167:
+		dbg("Registering bus=%x dev=%x hp_slot=%x sun=%x "
+			"slot_device_offset=%x\n",

Quoted strings that appear as messages in userspace and can be
grepped, should not be split across multiple lines.

See: https://lore.kernel.org/lkml/20120203052727.GA15035@leaf/

